snippet.title: NEW Pangya M Trailer「팡야M」
snippet.description:
https://www.patreon.com/PapelPodCast
Support us on Patreon and gain access to special rewards!

Pangya M is the Korean launch version of Pangya Mobile, which will be coming sometime 2020. With many new improvements over the test version launched in Thailand and closed last year.

Tell us what you think in the comment section below, and make sure to Subscribe and hit that 🔔 to keep up-to-date with everything Pangya.
